OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland will have a dry and
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy day after some early
OL,7,Fbrightness. Dry across Orkney with
OL,8,Fsome morning sunshine, but clouding
OL,9,Fover this afternoon. Light
OL,10,Fnortheasterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry
OL,13,Falthough fairly cloudy. Then the rest
OL,14,Fof the night will remain dry but with
OL,15,Fa good deal of cloud at times. Light
OL,16,Fnortheasterly winds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FStaying dry with cloud
OL,19,Fthinning to allow some bright or sunny
OL,20,Fintervals by afternoon. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
