OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FLittle change. Remaining dry with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,8,Fsunny periods. Light winds.
